bc857343-7780-497e-a0b1-95f2dfe00d78	https://www.eluocnc.com/ko/works_detail.asp?idx=155	ELUOCNC	Careers\nContact\nCompany Profile\nKR\nEN\nIFC MALL\nS.I.VILLAGE\nInnisfree\nParadise\nEmart\nKT\nL'Oréal\nLa Roche Posay\nNovita\nFinance\n10\n10\nDive into the\nInfinite Joys of\nIFC MALL\n01\n10\nThe Renewal of IFC MALL Website, the Landmark\nof Yeouido’s Integrated Shopping and Culture.\nIFC MALL, in collaboration with ELUO, has revitalized its website to offer an enhanced shopping experience to its customers. By focusing on a user-centered UI/UX and strengthening the visual design, we have successfully encapsulated IFC MALL's unique charm within the digital space.\nWe utilized the crystal shape of the IFC MALL logo as an irregular design element and incorporated the brand’s signature colors to emphasize a youthful and dynamic image. The color-coded floor guides and real-time store updates improve information accessibility, significantly enhancing customer convenience.\nELUO continues to maintain a strong partnership with IFC MALL, ensuring the stable operation of the website post-launch.\n2023 Web Awards Korea -\nShopping Center Grand Prize\nThe Renewal of\nIFC MALL Website\nClick here for details\nnext\nA Distinctive\nExperience with\nPremium Brands\n02\n10\nShinsegae International's\nPremier Digital Platform: S.I.VILLAGE.\nS.I.VILLAGE, the premium lifestyle shopping platform by Shinsegae International, showcases a meticulously curated selection of fashion, beauty, and living brands. This platform redefines the e-commerce landscape, offering customers a unique and differentiated value through its expertly curated brand offerings and content.\nAs the design partner for S.I.VILLAGE, ELUO is responsible for overseeing all aspects of the platform's visual and user experience design. By crafting immersive and engaging shopping experiences at every customer interaction point, ELUO elevates the platform's premium stature and strengthens its overall brand identity.\nThe premium\nlifestyle shopping\nplatform\nComprehensive\nDesign Operation\nof S.I.VILLAGE\nClick here for details\nnext\nAll-New Innisfree\nDigital Platform\n03\n10\nA Renewal of Innisfree’s\nShopping Mall and App.\nIn 2023, Innisfree embarked on a major rebranding journey, redefining its brand image and presenting a fresh new face to its customers. ELUO successfully partnered with Innisfree to revamp its official online mall and shopping app, and continues to manage the platform's operations today.\nWith the rebranding, Innisfree’s commerce platform underwent a significant redesign, offering a vibrant and personalized shopping experience through dynamic beauty content and tailored recommendations. ELUO remains dedicated to driving the evolution of Innisfree’s digital presence, ensuring the brand's reputation continues to shine.\nWon Two Awards at\n2023 Web and App Awards\nInnisfree’s\nE-Commerce Renewal\nand Maintenance\nClick here for details\nnext\n1\n2\n3\n4\n5\n6\nParadise\nHotel & Resort\n04\n10\nImpeccable\nDigital Experience,\nParadise Group\nParadise Group has grown into a global tourist landmark with the aim of being a ‘Destination Creator’ to achieve the highest level of customer satisfaction through its finest luxury services. ELUO team crafted a website with four key concepts of its corporate philosophy — Rest, Pleasure, Inspiration, and Sharing — in a bold way with carefully selected images and interactive design to improve their online presence. The new digital platform was successful in resonating with the passion and authenticity of Paradise’s value throughout Paradise Group, Paradise City, Paradise Casino, and Paradise Hotel Busan.\nThe\nDestination\nCreator\nFresh Approach to Corporate Blog\nParadise Group\nBlog Design\nRenewal\nClick here for details\nnext\nEmart’s\nInnovation\nPartner\nSince 2012\n05\n10\nELUO C&C has brought\ntangible results and\ncontinuous evolution\nfor Emart.\nOur partnership with Emart, the largest retailer and most popular supermarket chain in Korea, goes back to 2012 when Emart strategically prepared for the future shift of customers’ shopping. ELUO’s digital marketing strategy has become the primary driver of building up Emart digital culture.\nSince 2012, we’ve been providing exceptional ITO services for 14 Emart’s mobile web/app channels to deliver great CX experience at all stages of their customer journey. The significant outcomes — effective digital solutions at scale to drive compelling customer experience, intelligent operations, and smart supply chain management — have proved ELUO’s dedication and hard work.\nContactless Retail Strategy\nEmart Marketing App\nRenewal\nClick here for details\nOperations & Marketing\nEmart Web/ App\nManagement\nClick here for details\nEmart O2O Marketing Service\nScan-and-Deliver\nScan-and-See Info\nClick here for details\nEmart Electronman\nAR Game\nTouch Attack\nClick here for details\nContactless Retail Strategy\nEmart Marketing App\nRenewal\nClick here for details\nOperations & Marketing\nEmart Web/ App\nManagement\nClick here for details\nEmart O2O Marketing Service\nScan-and-Deliver\nScan-and-See Info\nClick here for details\nEmart Electronman\nAR Game\nTouch Attack\nClick here for details\nContactless Retail Strategy\nEmart Marketing App\nRenewal\nClick here for details\nOperations & Marketing\nEmart Web/ App\nManagement\nClick here for details\nEmart O2O Marketing Service\nScan-and-Deliver\nScan-and-See Info\nClick here for details\nEmart Electronman\nAR Game\nTouch Attack\nClick here for details\nScan Pay Go\nVIP Benefits\nSmart Order\nCustomer Satisfaction Survey\ne-Stamp\nScan-and-Deliver\nScan-and-See Info\nEmart TV\nEmart Music\nEmart Refrigerator\nnext\nKT’s\nTrustworthy\nPartner\n06\n10\nWith the help\nof our actionable insights,\nKT has outperformed\nin the fast-moving\ntelecommunications industry.\nELUO C&C has a long and fruitful partnership with KT, Korea’s largest comprehensive communications operator whose passion is to become the most valuable global brand with a customer-first strategy. With ‘customer-centric’ as the top priority, we’ve helped KT grow above and beyond their expectations from the first project in 2013. Since then, KT has designated our marketing team for multiple projects — KT.com, KT Shop, KT Direct, etc.\nNow, ELUO team is ready to be at the forefront with KT to guide customers through 5G innovation service to leverage the value of KT’s brand power. For KT’s digital transformation, we will build a better digital platform with powerful marketing strategies, and more personalized content services based on the customer’s lifestyle, technology-based innovations, and the latest UX design trends.\nTrustworthy Marketing Partner\nKT.com & KT Shop\nOperations\nClick here\nfor KT.com\nproject\nClick here\nfor KT Shop\nproject\nOnline Shopping Mall for Telecom\nKT Direct\nWeb Development\nClick here for details\nContactless Mobile Shopping\nKT\n‘One-Minute Order,\nOne-Hour Delivery’\nClick here for details\nnext\nL'Oréal Group’s\nCommunication\nPartner\n07\n10\nELUO C&C understands\nthe DNA of L'Oréal’s business\nthat aims to move and\nshape the world.\nL'Oréal formulated a business strategy — Universalization — to respect the diversity from different backgrounds and cultures, and pursue its mission of ‘Beauty for All’. To support the L'Oréal’s vision, ELUO team has played an increasingly vital role as a digital strategy partner.\nAlmost all of L'Oréal Korea’s e-commerce platforms are supported by Demandware and Sitecore. Due to our extensive experience and know-how in operating those platforms, we’ve provided a consistent brand experience to local customers while supporting unexpected technical issues.\nAs part of our multichannel sales strategy, ELUO team adopted the integrated sales channel of Shop-in-Shop (SiS) ecommerce platform to meet current demands of the market and therefore, it drove profitable customer action.\nL'Oréal Korea’s Digital\nConsulting Partner\nfor its Digital Transformation\nLancôme\nAnnual maintenance & improvement for its global e-commerce platform and the official online shopping mall operated by Damendware\n2017 ~\nYves Saint Lauren\nAnnual maintenance & improvement for its global e-commerce platform and the official online shopping mall operated by Damendware\n2019 ~\nShu Uemura\nAnnual maintenance for the brand site, and its Shop-in-Shop(SIS) sites integrated into major shopping malls such as Lotte, CJ, and Shinsegae, etc.\n2018 ~ 2021\nL'Oréal Paris\nAnnual maintenance & development for the hybrid branding of its brand and commerce channel, and the marketing platform\n2015 ~\nClick here for details\nMaybelline New York\nAnnual maintenance & development for its global e-commerce platform and the brand site operated by Sitecore\n2016 ~\nClick here for details\nLa Roche Posay\nAnnual maintenance & development for the official online shopping mall of La Roche Posay, dema cosmatic brand\n2018 ~\nClick here for details\nnext\nInspirational\ne-commerce Platform\nfor La Roche Posay\n08\n10\nWe created a digital space\nto maximize\nits global brand value.\nOver 40 years, La Roche-Posay defines its mission to improve people’s lives with sensitive skins by placing its expertise at the heart of its products. Our experienced team created a digital space where customers can experience the La Roche Posay’s brand, not just their products. We renewed the e-commerce site for La Roche-Posay to build more authentic and profitable relationship with their customers by effectively delivering the purpose, goals, and intention of its innovative skincare solutions.\nLa Roche Posay:\nWe Create\nBrand Value\nBeyond Products.\nClick here for details\nBeyond Web Management\nDigital Marketing for\nLa Roche Posay\nClick here for details\nnext\nRepositioning\nNovita Commerce\nas a Premium\nBrand\n09\n10\nA ELUO team of experts\npowered up Novita's\ne-commerce platform.\nKohler Novita is a new company created by\nNovita and Kohler, a luxury bathroom and kitchen\nbrand. Novita incorporates the philosophy of\nKohler’s 150 years of know-how and innovative\ntechnology into its designs. With such leading\nedge design and innovation, Novita becomes\na global leader in manufacture of kitchen and\nbath products. Novita also has set a new trend\nfor Korea’s high-tech bathroom standard.\nTeam ELUO developed Novita’s brand commerce\nsite to effectively delivers its intention to improve\ncustomers’ lifestyle experience with its high-end\nbath products. We also created a digital space\nwhere users can interact with its premium brand\nby portraying the Novita’s philosophy of ‘Clean,\nComfort, and Minimal’ design with content\nstorytelling and visual communication strategy.\nAfter successfully completing its website\ndevelopment project, our team has continued to\nimprove a user experience with a seamless UI/UX\nwhen providing its annual web maintenance services.\nThink Better!\nNOVITA\nINNOVATIVE\nE-COMMERCE SITE\nClick here for details\nnext\nTransforming\nthe Financial\nLandscape\n10\n10\nAt ELUO, we're pioneering the digital\nfinancial revolution in partnership\nwith industry leaders such as\nKB Kookmin Bank, Hana Bank,\nand Korea Investment & Securities.\nKorea Investment & Securities\n: M.ZIP is an innovative investment insight platform within Korea Investment & Securities' trading service app. This platform, specifically designed for the MZ generation, delivers engaging and contemporary financial content that is easily digestible even for first-time investors. At ELUO, we created this content based on our in-depth understanding of the MZ generation and user-friendly financial services. We also provide ongoing annual website maintenance as its digital partner.\nHana Bank\n: The 100-year Living Trust Center by Hana Bank is a trust-based asset management platform, providing comprehensive inheritance solutions. As trust becomes a significant financial trend in our era of longevity, it's crucial to provide accurate and valuable information to users. Rising to this challenge, ELUO skillfully crafted the Living Trust Center website, demystifying complex financial products and bringing clarity to users.\nKB Kookmin Bank\n: We've reshaped the way users interact with KB Kookmin Bank's digital content by introducing a unique yet user-friendly interface. ELUO thoughtfully curated the bank's financial product guides and informational content, employing innovative designs that feature lively illustrations, diagrams, and other visual elements. This creative approach, combined with our empathetic UX writing, bridges the gap between users and financial information, fostering a stronger, more meaningful connection.\nELUO Financial Project Development\nSimplifying Your\nFinancial Experience for\nGreater Convenience\nHana Bank\nProject\nKB Kookmin\nBank Project\nKorea Investment\n& Securities Project\nNHN KCP\nProject\nKorea Investors\nService Project\nInitech\nProject\nELUO Financial Project Development\nSimplifying Your\nFinancial Experience for\nGreater Convenience\nHana Bank\nProject\nKB Kookmin\nBank Project\nKorea Investment\n& Securities Project\nNHN KCP\nProject\nKorea Investors\nService Project\nInitech\nProject\nELUO Financial Project Development\nSimplifying Your\nFinancial Experience for\nGreater Convenience\nHana Bank\nProject\nKB Kookmin\nBank Project\nKorea Investment\n& Securities Project\nNHN KCP\nProject\nKorea Investors\nService Project\nInitech\nProject\nnext\ntop	eluocnc	works	{"scraped_at": "2026-03-17T01:30:57.457861+00:00"}	2026-03-20 02:18:18.116721+00	2026-03-20 02:18:18.116721+00
